#: edcat_root/pages/templates/base.html:18
#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:3
msgid "EDCAT"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/base.html:27
msgid "Language"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/base.html:52
msgid "Login"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:15
msgid "Welcome to our new website!"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:16
msgid "We're adjusting our system to make our services available in this space."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:18
msgid "CuReMAIn"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:19
msgid "(Customer Relationship Maganer with AI)"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:20
msgid ""
"Your company's relationship with its customers is the foundation for new "
"business and maintaining\n"
"its presence in today's competitive market."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:22
msgid ""
"With our AI-powered customer tracking system, this task, which requires "
"highly skilled personnel,\n"
"can be optimized by using intelligent queries to your databases and "
"product documentation."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:25
msgid "RAGA"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:26
msgid "(Retrieval-Augmented Generation Agent)"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:27
msgid "We develop custom agents to automatically respond to your customers."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:28
msgid ""
"Based on a database, we can develop an agent that answers specific "
"questions collected from\n"
"previous experiences with the CuReMAIn system or from a product manual "
"manufactured by the company."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:31
msgid "CybSeS"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:32
msgid "(Cyber Security Supremacy)"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:33
msgid ""
"Cybersecurity has entered a new era in 2025, where artificial "
"intelligence can be used as a\n"
"shield, but unfortunately, it is also used as a sword on a digital "
"battlefield that is becoming increasingly\n"
"sophisticated every day."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:36
msgid ""
"We have the expertise and tools to ensure the security of your data in "
"this new battleground."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:39
msgid "ConSISO"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:40
msgid "(Consulting for ISO)"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:41
msgid "Consulting for the implementation of ISO 27001 and 42001 standards."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:42
msgid ""
"Preparing a company for ISO certification requires the creation of a "
"series of documents, the\n"
"planning of various control procedures, and the verification of their "
"effectiveness."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:44
msgid ""
"We have a qualified technical team to provide the necessary consultancy "
"to achieve success in\n"
"first or second-party certification."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:47
msgid "TOPS"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:48
msgid "(Total On Premisses Support)"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:49
msgid "Consulting for implementing your company's IT infrastructure."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:50
msgid ""
"Even if you use our cloud solutions, you will still need a computer "
"network infrastructure\n"
"installed in your company so that your employees can perform their tasks."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:52
msgid ""
"We offer consulting services for this implementation, from the basics, "
"such as providing quality\n"
"electricity, which is the minimum necessary for the proper functioning of"
" all systems, to cloud migration and learning\n"
"how to use your systems in that environment."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:55
msgid ""
"If you're like some of our clients who insist on keeping your entire "
"infrastructure offline,\n"
"don't worry, we have solutions for you too."
msgstr ""

